      SOURCE #latest_LockedDate
        #// This method returns the latest date of which either the Entity's Period was Locked by the Admin or User
        #// or the latest date the Entity's transactions was locked.
        #// This method is mostly used to determin from where the last data can be deleted and re-imported,
